  "notes": "Pipeline 02: Discover\n- Polls expand_queue for queued companies\n- Runs 3 SearXNG searches per company\n- Fetches top 6 pages via Browserless\n- Gemini Flash extracts supply chain claims\n- Inserts raw claims into PostgreSQL\n- Triggers 03-challenge"
